Package Conditions.Converter

Class Summary
ConditionConverter description: this class implements a Converter, converting objects of classes of the package "Conditions" (that represent "real life conditions") into objects of classes of the package "AsbruConditions" (that represent the conditions in exactly that format that is defined at the dtd of the Asgard/Asbru Instead of using a Converter that distinguishes the different classes, i implemented the method to convert the condition directly in the different condition classes; this method makes it more difficult to change the Converter-Implementation, but in this scenario using this pattern is more efficient author: Christian Hinterer
